{"tid":1283759,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當未廢除到功能組別的時候","createTime":"2019-07-04T02:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T04:02:37.000Z","uid":227523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7771a2a1f16d8eb458662ee63200a2e7c6c0b0f5","tid":1283759,"uid":227523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:03:24.000Z","msg":"教育界，社福界，法律界<br />\n你地有冇副業秘撈，可能轉到你嘅功能組別啊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dctH3Pj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdctH3Pj.jpg&h=888c8465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hn7hSHF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhn7hSHF.jpg&h=4c120ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/drLbW9m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdrLbW9m.jpg&h=b502f67f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢三個功能組別守得住有餘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgUsvuF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgUsvuF.jpg&h=8ead5083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HBuL1Bn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHBuL1Bn.jpg&h=2800743d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有機會轉到功能組別就救呢兩個。<br />\n<br />\n同埋可唔可以搞多啲註冊文體藝等社團，讓我們多啲票？<br />\n<br />\n當然長遠係廢咗個功能組別"},{"pid":"4d367caeb729f2f0069cf32006672259dc8daea7","tid":1283759,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:12:18.000Z","msg":"重奪議會 人民發聲"},{"pid":"b8dffa71cce4ba20d3c98a4afb02a53fe7b27983","tid":1283759,"uid":227523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:25:30.000Z","msg":"諗諗佢"},{"pid":"f21a46ed19f4b7bb1028e2dbdefaed0f015382cf","tid":1283759,"uid":262154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:02:37.000Z","msg":"首先要專攻建制個人票組別:<br />\n1)工程界<br />\n2)建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界<br />\n叫所有工程師/建築師/測量師記住要加入相關專業組織同登記做功能組別選民<br />\n以下泛民(或半泛民)既個人票組別都要留心，唔好跌咗個議席<br />\n1)醫學界<br />\n2)會計界<br />\n3)資訊科技界<br />\n特別係IT!因為未必個個有加入專業組織做選民﹗<br />\n再加埋比較穩陣既法律界、教育界、社會福利界、衛生服務界同3席超級區議會，咁總共會有12席<br />\n當地區直選有60%議席，即係21席，咁總數有33席<br />\n<br />\n有少少可能再搶攻既功能組別係:<br />\n1)飲食界<br />\n2)進出口界<br />\n3)批發及零售界<br />\n4)紡織及製衣界<br />\n5)體育 藝術 文化 演藝<br />\n6) 勞工<br />\n有朋友係做呢啲行業既小東主，叫佢一定一定要做選民<br />\n有無巴打可以開始就住呢啲組別點登記做選民做文宣？<br />\n<br />\n一檔整合所有界別<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1BEIuxzPT8gQ-9VJRlxkWqxdwyw1K3uCP/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1BEIuxzPT8gQ-9VJRlxkWqxdwyw1K3uCP%2Fview&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O8fSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=08ddf348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1BEIuxzPT8gQ-9VJRlxkWqxdwyw1K3uCP/view</a>"}]}